text: Taskin Ahmed Tazim is a cricketer from Bangladesh. He plays for the Bangladesh national cricket team. He was born on April 3, 1995. On 17 June 2014, playing against India, he became the first Bangladeshi cricketer to take 5 wickets in ODI debut. == References == == Other websites == Category:Living people Category:1995 births Category:Cricketers from Dhaka
